{"tid":430777,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【蝗蟲柒出世界系例】強國客火葬場當佛寺影相？ 網民：大吉利是！","createTime":"2017-10-10T06:03:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T07:21:28.000Z","uid":76713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ad593600ed4f9ecf77fc8727dced88ff78d29354","tid":430777,"uid":76713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T06:03:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171010/large/1507598813_24f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171010%2Flarge%2F1507598813_24f3.jpg&h=e1d5341d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n泰華微信朋友圈近日熱傳中國遊客在泰國火葬場拍照，被嘲將火葬場當佛寺。有內地網民質疑，泰國網民為甚麼能確定拍照的遊客就是中國人？反正圖片寫上泰文說明：「<span style=\"color: red;\">不知道怎麼和中國人說，這裏，是燒屍房（火葬場）</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n泰國網民嘲諷：「泰國寺廟建築或佛像根本不適合拍照，這回他們還挑了個這麼吉（晦）祥（氣）的地方拍照，真是大吉利是啊！」還將圖片發送comedys Thailand，寫上：「這些圖片我不願一個人看，讓大家笑一下」。<br />\n網民指，泰國寺廟不單是用來弘揚佛法和旅遊觀光，還有其他用途，例如舉辦葬禮，焚燒屍體，將骨灰安置在寺廟圍牆上。泰國民眾去世後，屍體或將交由寺廟眾僧舉辦葬禮法會，不間斷念誦佛經結束後，屍體將被送往「燒屍房」火化。「燒屍房」這一名字雖然和「寺廟」相比有些俗，但在外人看起來，該類建築和寺廟還真的區別不大。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20171010/57312267\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20171010%2F57312267&d=6EIVBcTCt3Z5UoWiU1NYWcP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=5c1b0120\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20171010%2F57312267&h=2d746e54\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20171010/57312267</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d774f52370a8a170b26b9acda2320d4efa33800e","tid":430777,"uid":131064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T06:49:37.000Z","msg":"阿彌陀佛"},{"pid":"1d1fba5575f5f049f690831af1cbebcbaf248e12","tid":430777,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T07:21:28.000Z","msg":"有衰野嗰陣：你地點確定佢係中國人？"}]}